{"tid":299132,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【太刻薄加價】大家樂部份產品近月已加價2至4%","createTime":"2017-06-26T23:30:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-28T17:29:43.000Z","uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d190598b1c8ae59ca372da94092dbd29bd20d5a6","tid":299132,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T23:30:30.000Z","msg":"不過本報發現，大家樂部份產品售價已於近月加價2%至4%。<br />\n<br />\n以大家樂「慢煮咖喱牛腩飯」為例，今年2月單價為46元，但今日記者所見餐牌已調整為48元，加幅達4.35%；<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而「一哥焗豬扒飯」套餐（連飲品）亦由45元升至46元，<br />\n<br />\n四寶飯套餐（連飲品）則由43元升至44元，兩者加幅達2%。<br />\n<br />\n至於大快活，現時咖喱牛腩飯（連飲品）及焗豬扒飯單價分別是47元及41元，而四寶飯單價則是38元，<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而大家樂產品單價仍較大快活為高。"},{"pid":"9003fe2c6a3876f43b0b27f4d8d8cf295b939885","tid":299132,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T07:25:08.000Z","msg":"老實講根本度度都加價"},{"pid":"9f03f4ce5b80009f9d028b5540e002ad330fe1e6","tid":299132,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T07:25:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"907eaea23325b1f09ee0e35a762120f6339d60e2","tid":299132,"uid":25221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T07:26:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"732b40b7800290e3a2a5768e8894709ce936c0c1","tid":299132,"uid":98386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T08:11:29.000Z","msg":"食M記唔洗煩 反正大交鑊咪又係劣食"},{"pid":"141fa68d8f1aba87beb5688b24406cabc267aa24","tid":299132,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T17:29:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}